data.description: Seller to give a carpet credit of $3000  Previous Street of Dreams custom floor plan w/ TWO primary suites (one on main & one on upper), private and secluded backyard (set up high above the street) that is perfect for your leisurely Sunday morning coffee under the retractable awning or under the cozy pergola area on the expansive patio. Chef-friendly kitchen w/ black stainless appliances and walk-in pantry! Semi-circle breakfast nook with a custom bank of windows. Large Tuff Shed wired for a home shop or office. Friendly low-traffic neighborhood with sidewalks. Energy-saving solar panels; Jack-n-Jill bath upstairs. Open House 11-4-23 @1:30-3:30pm
